NVIDIA Nemotron Streaming ASR model
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

This add-on downloads and uses at runtime the ONNX export of the
NVIDIA Nemotron 3.5 Streaming ASR (0.6B) model:

  HuggingFace: nub235/nemotron-3.5-asr-streaming-onnx
  Original:    nvidia/nemotron-asr-streaming-multilingual-0.6b

The original model is © NVIDIA Corporation and is licensed under the
NVIDIA Open Model License:

  https://www.nvidia.com/en-us/agreements/enterprise-software/nvidia-open-model-license/

The ONNX export is a derivative work of the original NVIDIA model and
is distributed under the same NVIDIA Open Model License.

The model weights are not bundled with this add-on; they are downloaded
from HuggingFace at first boot and stored in /data/models.
